item.description:
People who are interested in living a healthy life and Chinese food may join this discussion. Let's share our ideas about some healthy Chinese food: how to chose and cook. Exercising doesn't mean that you have go to a GYM everyday and we could learn a few tips from each others. Of course, share any topics you would like regarding of healthy living.

The discussion will be led by Jennifer Zhang, who was a doctor in China before coming to the state. For more questions, please contact to Jennifer. Thanks!
